<h1>$Text{"OTRS Test Page"}</h1>

<hr>

<b>dynamic test</b><br>

<p>

<dtl set $Data{"Test1"} = "German">
a) Set $Data{\"Test1\"} = "$Data{"Test1"}"
<br>
Echo ($Text{\"Lock\"}): $Text{"Lock"}
<br>

<dtl if ($Text{"Lock"} eq "Lock") { $Data{"Test1"} = "English"; }>
b) if ($Text{\"Lock\"} eq "Lock") { $Data{\"Test:\"} = "English"; }<br>

Result: $Data{"Test1"}
</p>

<p>
<dtl set $Data{"Test1"} = "lala">
c) Set $Data{\"Test1\"} = "$Data{"Test1"}"
<br>

<dtl if ($Data{"Test1"} ne "hallo!") { $Data{"Test1"} = "hallo!!"; }>
d) if ($Data{\"Test1\"} ne "hallo!") { $Data{\"Test1\"} = "hallo!!"; }
<br>

Result: $Data{"Test1"}
</p>

<hr>

